# File: .cursor/rules/lint-failure-handling.mdc
---
description: Linting retries and failure protocol
alwaysApply: true
---

If `npx tsc` or `npm run lint` fails, retry up to 3 times only. If issues persist, state the unresolved problems and request permission to bypass. Avoid looping indefinitely.